---
import GlobalShell from '../components/layouts/GlobalShell.astro';
import AppHead from './_app-head.astro';
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <AppHead />
  </head>
  <body>
    <GlobalShell>
  <div
    id="home-main-hover"
    class="home-main-hover flex flex-1 items-center justify-center px-6 md:px-8"
  >
    <div class="flex w-full max-w-2xl flex-col items-center gap-6 text-center">
      <div class="h-32 w-32 rounded-full border border-[color:var(--border-subtle)] bg-slate-900/60 shadow-md shadow-slate-900/50" />

      <h1 class="w-full text-2xl font-extrabold tracking-[0.12em] uppercase text-[color:var(--text-main)] break-words md:text-4xl md:tracking-[0.2em]">
        Wishawin Lertnawapan
      </h1>

      <div class="home-typewriter w-full space-y-3 text-sm leading-relaxed text-[color:var(--text-muted)] md:text-base">
        <p>
          Hi there &#128522;! My name is Ein, I'm a recent <span class="font-semibold text-[color:var(--text-main)]">Integrated Masters' engineering graduate from the University of Bristol</span>, currently based in London. Despite an engineering background, my interests lie at the intersection of <span class="font-semibold text-[color:var(--text-main)]">Data Science, Machine Learning</span>, and <span class="font-semibold text-[color:var(--text-main)]">Software Engineering</span>. I'm always working on projects that involve leveraging technologies to drive innovation.
        </p>
        <p>
          Currently, I aim to pursue a Master's degree in mathematical computation in London, while working towards credentials in
          <a
            href="https://www.wqu.edu/mscfe"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noreferrer"
            class="font-semibold text-[color:var(--accent)]"
          >
            Financial Engineering
          </a>
          at WQU and
          <a
            href="https://aws.amazon.com/certification/certified-machine-learning-engineer-associate/"
            target="_blank"
            rel="noreferrer"
            class="font-semibold text-[color:var(--accent)]"
          >
            AWS
          </a>, driven by the slightly impossible task of wanting to learn everything (and caffeine &#9749;).
        </p>
        <p>
          I thrive where I can work simultaneously with both data scientists and business analytics teams directly &mdash; bridging <span class="font-semibold text-[color:var(--text-main)]">technical decision-making and getting involved with models, while also communicating insights</span> effectively to help clients perform at their best. Through project-based work in academia and work experiences, I continue to explore various domains including full-stack development, serverless cloud development, and quantitative finance that supplement my data skills.
        </p>
        <p>
          Thanks for stopping by &#128075;
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    </GlobalShell>

    <script type="module" src="/src/scripts/homeEffects.ts"></script>
  </body>
</html>
